{"tid":1554162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【求人手置頂】文宣整合攻略","createTime":"2019-09-09T00:59:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T05:15:15.000Z","uid":92277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b08bdcf9bc27904e8cb51110d7acafdb52c68b36","tid":1554162,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T00:59:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">多謝大家唔想我用錢唔推我個5000蚊post... 依家重開一個，求人手置頂</span><br />\n<br />\n我都好對唔住大家我呢排開左啲標題黨post, 因為文宣真係好重要，唔好停留同溫層<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">失敗唔係無人撐，係因為無人知</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n文宣我認為係難道最低而又可以幫到成個運動既一件事。<span style=\"color: gold;\">其實整圖既巴打唔介意人地偷圖，只會怪人睇完唔forward! </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔識整圖既大家，我有三樣野希望大家幫幫手</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.分享去 Facebook IG Whatsapp Gp </span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n連登接觸面唔夠廣，而且留得係到既已經係跟得好貼既人。希望大家見到靚既文宣，由其<span style=\"color: red;\">行動post</span>，幫一幫手做多步，repost 埋上ig, facebook, WhatsApp 之類既社交評台。一人拉多一個人去遊行就已經多好多。<br />\n<br />\n原文：<br />\n<br />\n200萬人有幾多個真係睇連登<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1542401\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1542401</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2. 貼連儂牆</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n雖然依家科技發達，但仲有好多人無辦法係果到收到信息。平時我等車都會望到好多叔叔望下牆。其實佢真係好吸睛，都係直接文宣既好地方!<br />\n<br />\n**建議組隊進行，放工放學咪貼兩張。<br />\n**如要去廠印刷，落單要開新Account <br />\n<br />\n原post:<br />\n老母一句屌醒左我，駁唔到。。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1546699\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1546699</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n文宣組入！印刷都會出事！<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dPQbDT\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dPQbDT</a><br />\n#1 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3. Airdrop 比全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n0成本，直接塞信息比人，<span style=\"color: red;\">行動post 優先</span>。平時搭車，行街得閒無野做咪用下！<br />\n<br />\n原post: <br />\n<br />\nIPhone有個咁好用既功能點解要浪費<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1551471\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1551471</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ld9NuBN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLd9NuBN.jpg&h=2115e932&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WzQQsos.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWzQQsos.jpg&h=35463d3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bUOniu8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbUOniu8.jpg&h=ad130f69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命！光復之日，煲底相聚💛</span>"},{"pid":"4d386eb972557b39cbc5f0abf08dae06b17dabf0","tid":1554162,"uid":92277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T00:59:55.000Z","msg":"岩岩人鏈完 睇完醫生要番工了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90fdbbf512cfe2a577e4e6ed6564fd0f742311a2","tid":1554162,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:00:24.000Z","msg":"求大家幫推 文宣很重要<br />\n光復香港 缺一不可"},{"pid":"41e8cbe03afc385c427a56e5212988546d6dc8e8","tid":1554162,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:00:57.000Z","msg":"求人手置頂"},{"pid":"2c9578511fc65fef1afce8b16d0c3e180dae1927","tid":1554162,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:01:44.000Z","msg":"文宣人人都做到<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>每人拉多一個朋友 已經多好撚多</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"8cb834c5df68e66a850b136c89553a8819f583a1","tid":1554162,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:02:00.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"4d18bcc4837d53f5ef7bf80f0eccdcb23c340aa7","tid":1554162,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,